src:
AP Top News at 4:21 a.m. EST
06 Nov 2019, 05:00 by EndPlay
Dems flip Virginia; Kentucky governor race too close to call
AP sources: State Dept. worried about defending ambassador
US child survivors of Mexico ambush saved by courage, mother
Pro-Beijing lawmaker in Hong Kong stabbed while campaigning
Voters in US states decide on sanctuary city, Airbnb rentals
UK leader compares rival to Stalin at start of election
US diplomat acknowledges what Democrats call a quid pro quo
Beshear claims victory in Kentucky; Bevin refuses to concede
Republican wins competitive race for Mississippi governor
